ITEM 1 1031 ADJ1=29 VAL2=1645

ITEM 0 1112

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The sign describes the way the Money Exchange operates.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
	           Welcome to the Money Exchange.
	 We change gold, kragenmarks, shards, and darktars.
	  We ONLY make changes in units equal to 100 GOLD!
	          For a modest 15 percent fee.
	 ----------------------------------------------------
	        To start the exchange say "CHANGE"
	         Then follow the instructions....
	     Say the names of the moneies as requested.
	 Moneies changed GOLD, KRAGENMARKS, DARKTARS, SHARDS
	 ----------------------------------------------------
	 Current Rates of Exchange (subject to change at any time)
	            100 gold equals 300 shards
	            100 gold equals 10000 darktars
	            100 gold equals 1200  kragenmarks

*DESCRIPTION_END 

IFSAY CHANGE
  EQUAL FLAG1 0
  EQUAL FLAG2 0
  ECHO PLAYER The attendant nods to you and says, "Please state what currancy to change from."
  ECHO OTHERS The attendant nods to %N and says, "Please state what currancy to change from."
ENDIF

IFSAY GOLD
	IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
		EQUAL FLAG2 1
	ENDIF
	IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
		EQUAL FLAG1 1
		EQUAL FLAG2 0
		ECHO PLAYER The attendant nods to you and says, "Please state what currency to change to."
		ECHO OTHERS The attendant nods to %N and says, "Please state what currency to change to."
	ENDIF

ENDIF
IFSAY SHARDS
	IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
		EQUAL FLAG2 2
	ENDIF
	IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
		EQUAL FLAG1 2
		EQUAL FLAG2 0
		ECHO PLAYER The attendant nods to you and says, "Please state what currency to change to."
		ECHO OTHERS The attendant nods to %N and says, "Please state what currency to change to."
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY DARKTARS
	IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
		EQUAL FLAG2 3
	ENDIF
	IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
		EQUAL FLAG1 3
		EQUAL FLAG2 0
		ECHO PLAYER The attendant nods to you and says, "Please state what currency to change to."
		ECHO OTHERS The attendant nods to %N and says, "Please state what currency to change to."
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY KRAGENMARKS
	IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
		EQUAL FLAG2 4
	ENDIF
	IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
